flowRoot.flowPara: Dashed lines are folders, solid lines are files (aka modules). Each module imports submodules below or to the right as indicated by solid lines. Modules in white are up and running, those in gray are planned for added functionality in the future.
Device Drivers are meant to handle communication with instruments
Control Logic modules handle data from the network or local disk as well as controlling devices via appropriate drivers.
User interface modules should be top-level and rely heavily on Control Logic modules.
